data.description: Stop looking! You found it!  This Eagleridge gem is perfect for your family and currently the most affordable home listed in the area!  Right away you are greeted by a lovely living room with warm colors, convenient main level half bathroom, and perfect kitchen with stainless steel appliances and even a gas range!  Upstairs consists of 4 bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master bedroom has a nice sized closet.  The basement is ready for future expansion for a family room, man cave, game room, or more bedrooms, whatever your heart desires.  The fully fenced large backyard has tons of possibilities and a dog run. Home is conveniently located to many amenities and just 30 minutes to Ft. Carson. Take a look before it's gone!
